      "id": "PopularPost323981",
      "post_content": "Such an awesome card. It's an uncommon that you can build a deck around. It's also awesome for boros because it gives you hastey battalion for the cost of a burn spell. He's also quite the beater himself. If you burn away their blocker(s), they will take massive damage.  \n  \nExcellent clamp engine in my [Tajic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tajic) EDH deck because the card draw fuels the burns, which fuel the clamp fodder, etc. Basically, lots of burns, and lots of card advantage.",
      "posted_by": "SAUS3",
