      "id": "PopularPost332013",
      "post_content": "I am very sad about the ruling on this card. I was running off the ruling given to me by a local judge at the prerelease (each instance of damage), which is also used by Forge. This card was another finisher when combined with Blasphemous Act (instead of just relying on Boros Reckoner), but after reading the ruling it is just a small way of generating advantage which comes in way too late.",
